movie.title: One Must Fall
movie.description_intro: A horror-comedy slasher set in the 80s about a woman wrongfully fired from her office job and forced to take on a temporary job on a crime scene cleanup crew. With a maniacal serial killer on the loose leaving them lots of work, did he ever leave the scene of the crime?

movies.title: Down to Earth
movies.summary: Upset about a new Broadway musical's mockery of Greek mythology, the goddess Terpsichore comes down to earth and lands a part in the show. She works her charms on the show's producer and he incorporates her changes into the show. Unfortunately, her changes also produce a major flop.

movies.title: Ace Ventura: Pet Detective Jr.
movies.summary: The son of an eccentric detective steps into his father's shoes after his mother is wrongly arrested for stealing a baby panda.

movies.title: Everything You Always Wanted to Know About Sex * But Were Afraid to Ask
movies.title_english: Everything You Always Wanted to Know About Sex * But Were Afraid to Ask
movies.title_long: Everything You Always Wanted to Know About Sex * But Were Afraid to Ask (1972)
movies.summary: Seven segments related to one another only in that they all purport to be based on sections of the book by David Reuben. The segments range from "Do Aphrodisiacs Work?" in which a court jester gives an aphrodisiac to the Queen and is, in the end, beheaded to "What Happens During Ejaculation?" in which we watch "control central" during a successful seduction.

movies.title: Whisky
movies.summary: When his long-lost brother resurfaces, Jacobo, desperate to prove his life has added up to something, looks to scrounge up a wife. He turns to Marta, an employee at his sock factory, with whom he has a prickly relationship.
